quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  38,52,wendhm nisa' qasirat 'absarihina ealaa 'azwajahuna mtsawyat fi alsn
  38,53,"hdha alnaeim hu maa tueadun bh- 'ayuha almtqwn- yawm alqyamt, 'iinah larzqna lkm, lays lah fna' wala anqtae"
  38,54,"hdha alnaeim hu maa tueadun bh- 'ayuha almtqwn- yawm alqyamt, 'iinah larzqna lkm, lays lah fna' wala anqtae"
  38,55,"hdha aldhy sabaq wasafah llmtqyn. wa'amaa almtjawzwn alhdd fi alkufr walmeasy, falahum sharun marjie wmsyr, wahu alnaar yuedhdhabwn fyha, tghmrhm min jmye jwanbhm, fabis alfrash frashhm"
  38,56,"hdha aldhy sabaq wasafah llmtqyn. wa'amaa almtjawzwn alhdd fi alkufr walmeasy, falahum sharun marjie wmsyr, wahu alnaar yuedhdhabwn fyha, tghmrhm min jmye jwanbhm, fabis alfrash frashhm"
  38,57,"hadha aleadhab ma'an shadid alhrart, wsdyd sayil min ajsad 'ahl alnaar flyshrbwh, walahum eadhab akhar min hdha alqbyl asnaf walwan"
  38,58,"hdha aleadhab ma'an shadid alhrart, wsdyd sayil min ajsad 'ahl alnaar flyshrbwh, walahum eadhab akhar min hdha alqbyl asnaf walwan"
  38,59,"wend tward altaghyn ealaa alnaar yashtm bedhm bedana, wayaqul bedhm lbed: hadhih jamaeat min 'ahl alnaar dakhlt mekm, fyjybwn: la mrhbana bhm, wala aitasaeat manaziluhum fi alnar, 'iinahum mqaswn hrr alnaar kama qasynaha"
  38,60,"qal fawj alatbae lltaghyn: bal 'antum la mrhbana bkm; lankm qddamtm lana skna alnaar l'idlalkm lana fi aldnya, fabis dar alaistiqrar jhnm"
  38,61,"qal fawj alatbae: rabana man adllana fi aldunya ean alhudaa fdaeif eadhabah fi alnar"
  38,62,"wqal altaghwn: ma balna la naraa maeana fi alnaar rijalana kunaa naeuduhum fi aldunya min al'ashrar alashqya'? hal thqyrna lahum wasthzawna bihim khta, 'aw 'anahum maeana fi alnar, lkn lm taqae ealayhim alabsar?"
  38,63,"wqal altaghwn: ma balna la naraa maeana fi alnaar rijalana kunaa naeuduhum fi aldunya min al'ashrar alashqya'? hal thqyrna lahum wasthzawna bihim khta, 'aw 'anahum maeana fi alnar, lkn lm taqae ealayhim alabsar?"
  38,64,'in dhlk min jidal 'ahl alnaar wkhsamhm haqa waqie la miryat fyh
  38,65,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iinama 'ana mundhir lakum min eadhab allah 'an yahila bkm; bsbb kfrkm bh, lays hunak 'ilh msthq llebadt 'iilaa allah whdh, fahu almtfrd bezmth wasmayh wsfath wafealh, alqhhar aldhy qhr kula shay' wghlbh"
  38,66,"malk alsmwat wal'ard wama baynahuma aleaziz fi antqamh, alghafaar ldhnwb man tab wa'anab 'iilaa mrdath"
  38,67,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iina hdha alquran khabar eazim alnfe. 'antum eanh ghafilun mnsrfwn, la taemalun bh"
  38,68,"ql -ayha alrswl- lqwmk: 'iina hdha alquran khabar eazim alnfe. 'antum eanh ghafilun mnsrfwn, la taemalun bh"
  38,69,"lays li eilm bakhtsam malayikat alsama' fi shan khalaq adm, lawla telym allah 'iyay, w'iyhawh 'ilya"
  38,70,"ma yuhi allah 'ily min eilm ma la eilm li bih 'iilaa li'aniy nadhir lakum min edhabh, mbyin lakum shreh"
  38,71,"adhkr lahum -ayha alrswl-: hin qal rabuk llmlaykt: 'iiniy khaliq bshrana min tyn. fa'iidha swwayt jasadih wkhlqh wanafakht fih alrwh, fdbt fih alhyat, fasjuduu lah sjwd tahiatan w'ikram, la sjwd eibadat wtezym; falebadt la takun 'illa lilah whdh. waqad hrram allah fi shryet al'islam alsujud llthyt"
  38,72,"adhkr lahum -ayha alrswl-: hin qal rabuk llmlaykt: 'iiniy khaliq bshrana min tyn. fa'iidha swwayt jasadih wkhlqh wanafakht fih alrwh, fdbt fih alhyat, fasjuduu lah sjwd tahiatan w'ikram, la sjwd eibadat wtezym; falebadt la takun 'illa lilah whdh. waqad hrram allah fi shryet al'islam alsujud llthyt"
  38,73,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun taeat wamtthala ghyr 'iblys; fa'iinah lm yasjud anafatan wtkbrana, wakan min alkafirin fi ealim allah teala"
  38,74,"fsjd almalayikat kuluhum 'ajmaeun taeat wamtthala ghyr 'iblys; fa'iinah lm yasjud anafatan wtkbrana, wakan min alkafirin fi ealim allah teala"
  38,75,"qal allah l'iblys: ma aldhy manaeak min alsujud liman akrmtuh fkhlqtuh bydya? 'astakbart ealaa adm, 'am kunt min almutakabirin ealaa rbk? wafi alayat 'iithbat sifat alydyn lilah tabarak wteala, ealaa alwajh allayq bih sbhanh"
  38,76,"qal 'iiblis meardana lrbh: lm asjd lh; li'anani 'afdal mnh, hayth khalaqtani min narin, wakhalaqtah min tyn. (walnar khayr min altyn)"
  38,77,"qal allah lh: fakhruj min aljanat fa'iinak mrjwm balqwl, mdhwr mlewn, wa'iina ealayk tardiin w'ibeady 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"
  38,78,"qal allah lh: fakhruj min aljanat fa'iinak mrjwm balqwl, mdhwr mlewn, wa'iina ealayk tardiin w'ibeady 'iilaa yawm alqyamt"
  38,79,"qal 'iblys: rbb fakhkhir ajly, wala thlkny 'iilaa hin tabeth alkhalq min qbwrhm"
  38,80,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak min almwkhkharyn 'iilaa yawm alwaqt almelwm, wahu yawm alnfkht al'uwlaa eindama tamut alkhlayq"
  38,81,"qal allah lh: fa'iinak min almwkhkharyn 'iilaa yawm alwaqt almelwm, wahu yawm alnfkht al'uwlaa eindama tamut alkhlayq"
  38,82,"qal 'iblys: fbeztk- ya rb- wezmtk ladlnn bani adam ajmeyn, 'iilaa man akhlstah minhum lebadtk, wesmtah min 'idlaly, falam tajeal li ealayhim sbyla"
  38,83,"qal 'iblys: fbeztk- ya rb- wezmtk ladlnn bani adam ajmeyn, 'iilaa man akhlstah minhum lebadtk, wesmtah min 'idlaly, falam tajeal li ealayhim sbyla"
  38,84,"qal allh: falhqq mny, wala 'aqul 'iilaa alhq, lamlan jahanam mink wamin dhrytk wamiman tabieak min bani adam ajmeyn"
  38,85,"qal allh: falhqq mny, wala 'aqul 'iilaa alhq, lamlan jahanam mink wamin dhrytk wamiman tabieak min bani adam ajmeyn"
  38,86,"ql -ayha alrswl- lhwla' almushrikin min qwmk: la 'atlub minkum ajrana 'aw jza'an ealaa daeawtukum whdaytkm, wala addaey amrana lays ly, bal 'atabie ma ywha 'ilya, wala 'atakalaf tkhrrusana waftra'an"
  38,87,"ma hdha alquran 'iilaa tadhkir lilealamin min aljini wal'ins, yatadhakarun bih ma yanfaeuhum min masalih dinahum wdnyahm"
  38,88,"wltelmn- 'ayuha almshrkwn- khabar hdha alquran wsdqh, hin yaghlb al'islam, wayadkhul alnaas fih afwajana, wkdhlk hin yaqae ealaykum aledhab, wtnqte eankum alasbab"
  39,1,"tnzyl alquran 'iinama hu min allah aleaziz fi qudratih wantqamh, alhakim fi tdbyrh wahkamh"
  39,2,"'ina 'anzalna 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- alquran yamur bialhaqi waledl, faebud allah whdh, wakhls lah jmye dynk"
  39,3,"'ala lilah wahdah alttaeat alttamat alsalmt min alshrk, waladhin 'ashrakuu mae allah ghyrh watakhadhuu min dunih awlya', qalu: ma naebud tilk alalihat mae allah 'iilaa ltshfe lana eind allh, wtqrbna eindah mnzlt, fakafaruu bdhlk; li'ana alebadt walshfaet lilah whdh, 'iina allah yafsil bayn almuminin almukhlasin walmushrikin mae allah ghyrh yawm alqiamat fima yakhtalifun fih min ebadthm, fyjazy kla bima ysthq. 'iina allah la yuafiq llhdayt 'iilaa alsirat almustaqim man hu mftr ealaa allh, kaffar biayatih whjjh"
  39,4,"lw 'arad allah 'an yatakhidh wldana lakhtar min mkhlwqath ma ysha', tnzzah allah wtqddas ean 'an yakun lah wld, fa'iinah alwahid alahd, alfard alsmd, alqhhar aldhy qhr khalaqah bqdrth, fkl shay' lah mtdhll khade"
  39,5,"khlq allah alsmwat wal'ard wama fihima balhq, yaji' biallayl wayudhhib balnhar, wyjy' bialnahar wayudhhib ballyl, wdhllal alshams walqamar biaintizam lmnafe alebad, kl minhuma yajri fi mdarh 'iilaa hin qiam alsae. 'ala 'iina allah aladhi faeal hadhih alafeal, wanem ealaa khalaqah bhdhh alnaeam hu aleaziz ealaa khlqh, alghafaar ldhnwb eibadih altaybyn"
  39,6,"khlqkm rbkm- 'ayuha alnas- min adm, wakhalaq minh zwjh, wakhalaq lakum min al'aneam thamaniat 'anwae dhkr‌ana wantha min al'iibil walbqr waldan walmez, yakhluqukum fi butun 'umahatikum twrana baed tawar min alkhalq fi zulumat albtn, walrhm, walmashimat, dhlkm allah aladhi khalaq hadhih alashya', rabukum almtfrd bialmalik almtwhd balalwhyt almsthq llebadt whdh, fkyf tedlwn ean eibadatih 'iilaa eibadat ghyrh min khlqh?"
  39,7,"'iina tkfru- 'ayuha alnas- birabikum walam tuminuu bh, walam tatabieuu rslh, fa'iinah ghny enkm, lays bihajat 'ilykm, wa'antum alfuqara' 'ilyh, wala yardaa lieibadih alkfr, wala yamuruhum bh, wa'iinama yardaa lahum shakar nieamah elyhm. wala tahmil nfs 'iithm nfs akhra, thuma 'iilaa rabukum msyrkm, fykhbrkm bemlkm, wyhasbkm elyh. 'iinah ealim bi'asrar alnufus wama tukhfi alsdwr"